表的代码预览业务-成本分类(OK)

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_costname')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_costname
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_costname */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_costname (
CostNameID int not null,
FieldName varchar(200) not null,
constraint PK_BUSI_COSTNAME primary key (CostNameID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('busi_costname') and minor_id = 0)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_costname'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'业务-成本分类(OK)',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_costname'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('busi_costname')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'CostNameID')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_costname', 'column', 'CostNameID'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'成本ID',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_costname', 'column', 'CostNameID'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('busi_costname')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'FieldName')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_costname', 'column', 'FieldName'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'字段名',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_costname', 'column', 'FieldName'
go
